{"tid":2477734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【清算港台】傳管理層抽起節目後將向員工追討製作費　港台：員工不當承付開支可徵附加費","createTime":"2021-04-06T13:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T15:21:38.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"9e300306361a15e80d2bde1e4d4c14f5ed99ede6","tid":2477734,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:46:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>播缸魚算啦李百全</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%B8%85%E7%AE%97%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0-%E5%82%B3%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B1%A4%E6%8A%BD%E8%B5%B7%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E5%BE%8C%E5%B0%87%E5%90%91%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E8%BF%BD%E8%A8%8E%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C%E8%B2%BB-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0-%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%8D%E7%95%B6%E6%89%BF%E4%BB%98%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF%E5%8F%AF%E5%BE%B5%E9%99%84%E5%8A%A0%E8%B2%BB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%258A%25BD%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E8%25A8%258E%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%25B2%25BB-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%2589%25BF%25E4%25BB%2598%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E9%2599%2584%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%25B2%25BB%2F&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=e7cf7997\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%258A%25BD%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E8%25A8%258E%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%25B2%25BB-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%2589%25BF%25E4%25BB%2598%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E9%2599%2584%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%25B2%25BB%2F&h=0f8ab35f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%B8%85%E7%AE%97%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0-%E5%82%B3%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B1%A4%E6%8A%BD%E8%B5%B7%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E5%BE%8C%E5%B0%87%E5%90%91%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E8%BF%BD%E8%A8%8E%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C%E8%B2%BB-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0-%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%8D%E7%95%B6%E6%89%BF%E4%BB%98%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF%E5%8F%AF%E5%BE%B5%E9%99%84%E5%8A%A0%E8%B2%BB/</a><br />\n<br />\n港台早前有節目的部分集數被抽起，消息指，如節目是因未能「過關」導致無法播出，涉事員工會被追討製作費作處分。港台回覆《立場》查詢時表示，港台作為政府部門，《公共財政條例》適用於港台員工，如政府認為有公務人員在受聘時不當地承付開支，可向該人徵收附加費。根據條例，有關附加費由財政司司長決定金額，從薪金或退休金等報酬扣除。<br />\n<br />\n《公共財政條例》列明，如公職人員受聘用時不當地承付開支，財政司司長可向該人徵收附加費並決定金額，及後由該人的每月薪金、工資或退休金扣除，其總額不得超過該月報酬的一半。被徵收者有權在獲通知後 30 日內，向行政長官提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士上月向《立場》表示，管理層有最新構思，表示如果《鏗鏘集》、《鏗鏘說》團隊拒絕按管理層建議修改節目內容，令節目無法「過關」，同時又未有可以頂替的「過關」節目出街，管理層就要問責，涉事員工可能會被追討製作費，而製作一集長約半小時的節目成本可高達 20 萬元。（詳見報道）"},{"pid":"72923343d8bdeabdbe61f4d0f3e2e6239cfe0652","tid":2477734,"uid":292292,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:49:10.000Z","msg":"被人清算緊，點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c618c047b80ac129c65f79bbfc1620ab5d97b9c","tid":2477734,"uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"2樓無尾bear #292292 歷史<br />\n<br />\n香港人, 輕鬆吓啦, follow 大波madam 有咩問題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488251</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZEZvcFwQHbu5kwyHyYrRhRZbz14M5ERW7vQkQpuhNa3x?filename=FjaoM5S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFjaoM5S.png&h=016403c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRrv3BaK